quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  28,22,"Nde o feewtunoo hella Madyana, o maaki: "Hino hasii ka Joomi am fewnirta lam, e laawol pocciingol ngol"."
  28,23,"Nde o hewtunoo ka …ìunndu Madyana, o tawi …óon dental yim…ìe, he…ìe njarna [daabeeji ma…ì…ìe], o tawi gaanin ma…ì…ìe, rew…ìe …ói…óo, no sogga [dammi ma…ì…ìe], o maaki: "Ko hol…óum habbi-…óon?" ∆Åe mb'i: "Min njarnataa haa aynoo…ìe …ìen nde'estoo, baaba amen, ko maw…óo nayeejo"."
  28,24,"O yarnani …ìe [dammi …óin], refti o huccitiri ka …óowdi, o maaki: "Joomi am, min ko njippin…óaa e am woo e mo∆¥∆¥ere, ko mi katonji…óo"."
  28,25,"Gooto e [jiw…ìe] …ìen ari e makko, homo yahra hersa, o wi'i: "Baaba am no nodde, fii yo o yo…ìe njo…ìdi kon ko njarnan-…óaa men". Tuma o hewtunoo ka [maw…óo] on, o sifanii mo fii [makko], o maaki: "Wota a hul, a da…óii yim…ìe too√±oo…ìe …ìen"."
  28,26,"Gooto e [jiw…ìe] …ìen wi'i: "∆≥ettu mo golle, yo baaba. Pellet, ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e mo ∆¥ettataa golle, ko doolnu…óo koolnii…óo"."
  28,27,"[Maw…óo] on maaki: "Mi…óo yi…ói desingol ma gooto e jiw…ìe am …ìen …óoo …ói…óo, e hoore yo a golla-nam duu…ìi jeetati. Si a timminii sappo, haray ko e sago maa; mi faalaaka sa…ótinannde ma. A tawat kam, si Alla ja…ìii, ko e mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen mi jeyaa"."
  28,28,"[Muusaa] maaki: "∆äum wonii hakkunde am e mon. Happu woo e majji …ói…ói, …ói mi huu…ìni, haray …ìi…óteede alanaa e kam. En wa…óii Alla pawtii…óo e ko wowlu…óen kon"."